- nih info <pkg> - synonym for nih search -9 n:e:<pkg>
- nih search -r doesn't work without -39
- nih refresh - copy pkg_summary.txt to pkg_summary-YYYYMMDD.txt
  and use such summaries for in 'nih clean-cache' and 'nih install'
- before update warn about missed binaries for installed packages
  (downgrade will not be possible)
- yesno_<type>=yes|no variables for yesno questions.
- save summary of installed packages to make downgrade possible
- use pkg_distbb for source-based update
